WEBVTT


00:00:00.237 --> 00:00:01.343
what are the requirements

00:00:01.344 --> 00:00:04.091
to apply to European Union volunteering

00:00:04.092 --> 00:00:06.301
the most important thing is that you have to live there

00:00:06.302 --> 00:00:07.592
in any of these countries

00:00:07.697 --> 00:00:09.840
and be over 18 years of age

00:00:09.841 --> 00:00:12.625
it is very very easy to apply and obviously

00:00:12.626 --> 00:00:13.898
worth the

00:00:13.899 --> 00:00:16.612
you can only choose European Union countries

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:18.018
the most fun

00:00:18.019 --> 00:00:20.024
and there are different volunteer times

00:00:20.025 --> 00:00:22.531
in addition to humanitarian aid and all that as well

00:00:22.532 --> 00:00:23.525
for example eh

00:00:23.715 --> 00:00:25.999
attending conservation area spaces

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.685
of animals or in

00:00:28.275 --> 00:00:30.662
helping new entrepreneurs and new projects
